          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Corrected for the attenuation by the 105Pd and the",
                " 197Au sample runs, respectively, for effects coming",
                " from the neutron self-shielding and multiple-scatte-",
                " ring, for the gamma-ray scattering and absorption in",
                " the sample, from the dependence of the gamma-ray",
                " detection efficiency on the gamma-ray source position,",
                " for the impurities in sample, and for the dead time.",
                " Corrections for the neutron self-shielding and mul-",
                " tiple-scattering were made by using a Monte-Carlo",
                " method, see REL-REF, K.Senoo+. Correction coeffs are",
                " given in Table 2 of main ref."
              ]
            }
          ],
